The paper discusses a system for distributed inference in latent variable models, which is a topic that falls under machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions the use of statistical modeling and parameter projection schemes, which are relevant to data analysis and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
